3423acc6a1e295569d7b","tid":424642,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>11%,你要寫明,當中仲要大部份都係無錢無權無勢果班人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你條命 你既財產 你既生產力都係共產黨架啵<br />\n香港地邊個叫做有權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把香港人爭住做猶太人啦<br />\n睇住自己既同胞入集中營<br />\n恥笑佢地不知天高地厚<br />\n<br />\n然後自己都入埋去集中營去死"},{"pid":"f904e0f481c7ea1887dcb2b929feb2377c9ca686","tid":424642,"uid":38671,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"最好笑係口講少人支持港獨<br />\n但又24小時係到反港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6dfb6aee1ce19ce9507ff41d39444a6411a5da","tid":424642,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"如果"},{"pid":"519f4d6d3801d578a0da5cc6be687a36acca902f","tid":424642,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b18f38fec05ae7eb628fb58af31c40650950a9ec","tid":424642,"uid":46644,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"841f291909eaa1471e5199cc2a952cb8d4ce92b4","tid":424642,"uid":86841,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffb68331905e91c4a0fbe7582782e86a42a965a8","tid":424642,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"支持港獨係小數<br />\n但反&quot;反港獨&quot;既人就好多"},{"pid":"2b9d8ba276767fa79198fd1d130f9b7e7419803d","tid":424642,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:18:19.000Z","ms